    "uuid": "49f3d9c0-2520-45a2-9f5f-494d9e7a6416.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.1.1\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will assign a lead node for each data provider submitting data to PDS",
    "requirement": "1.1.1"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "0178be71-7385-40dd-b979-c70c7cff8fdf.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.1.2\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will assign a lead individual, designated by the lead node, who is authorized to negotiate for PDS",
    "requirement": "1.1.2"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "2526ee0f-2294-46fb-bc5c-703144d45610.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.1.3\n\n### Requirement\nThe PDS lead node will delegate responsibility for subordinate contacts (e.g., instrument teams within a mission) to the appropriate PDS nodes",
    "requirement": "1.1.3"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "0631d417-a73e-4fea-a01e-792e259b4160.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.2.1\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will provide examples and suggestions on organization of data products, metadata, documentation and software",
    "requirement": "1.2.1"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "12c6562d-71d2-44ee-a366-df69abea672c.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.2.2\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will provide expertise in applying PDS standards",
    "requirement": "1.2.2"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "7f4448e2-b112-4d4d-9ff0-bc3ba1843083.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.2.3\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will provide expertise to support the design of scientifically useful archival data sets",
    "requirement": "1.2.3"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "b6f77727-9ee2-47b3-afee-6d984539e4fd.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.2.4\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will provide training to support the design of archival data sets for data providers on PDS standards, tools and services",
    "requirement": "1.2.4"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "d64d8bc0-632e-4223-bb84-b6f286bd2a59.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.2.5\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will provide training to develop and maintain staff expertise in data engineering, standards and tools",
    "requirement": "1.2.5"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "12487c37-536e-43f9-bf94-c489fbb741ca.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.3.1\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will provide examples of data management and archive plans (including interface documents, procedures, schedules and templates)",
    "requirement": "1.3.1"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "e40efe3a-5ebf-4423-b418-924cc7187f82.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.3.2\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will determine whether data management and archive plans and relevant interface documents meet PDS requirements",
    "requirement": "1.3.2"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "cd0c95b6-034c-4584-80fb-a37c6bd40671.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.3.3\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will provide criteria for validating archival products",
    "requirement": "1.3.3"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "31598faf-5492-421a-a11c-7b8608e11cfc.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.3.4\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will coordinate with the data providers to establish schedules for delivery of archival products to the PDS",
    "requirement": "1.3.4"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "c034e9f0-3f70-4183-a87d-577e353a78c7.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.3.5\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will coordinate with data providers to establish schedules for public release of archival products",
    "requirement": "1.3.5"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "2e47105b-9460-42d4-b6a6-25078d137332.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.4.1\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will define a standard for organizing, formatting, and documenting planetary science data",
    "requirement": "1.4.1"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "db4b526a-8638-4ec6-8398-04d4c5d15bef.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.4.2\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will maintain a dictionary of terms, values, and relationships for standardized description of planetary science data",
    "requirement": "1.4.2"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "ec915485-fdce-491d-afc1-627419733f85.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.4.3\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will define a standard grammar for describing planetary science data",
    "requirement": "1.4.3"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "cd54d484-90ef-4e04-aafc-3972e1446aff.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.4.4\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will establish minimum content requirements for a data set (primary and ancillary data)",
    "requirement": "1.4.4"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "e0a7af77-044c-41d3-b9bd-d7585fab1b3d.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.4.5\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will, for each mission or other major data provider, produce a list of the minimum components required for archival data",
    "requirement": "1.4.5"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "f7d03cf1-26fe-42c6-a9e3-40ae35bdad88.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.4.6\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will develop, publish and implement a process for managing changes to the archive standards",
    "requirement": "1.4.6"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "7ed10f48-94bd-496d-a110-18f44a8316b9.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.4.7\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will keep abreast of new developments in archiving standards",
    "requirement": "1.4.7"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "387486be-a85e-430f-abff-1353ec4b6156.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n1.5.1\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will provide tools to assist data producers in generating PDS compliant products",
    "requirement": "1.5.1"
  },
