    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n2.9.1\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will accept and distribute only those items which are not restricted by the International Traffic in Arms Regulations (ITAR)",
    "requirement": "2.9.1"
  },
