    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n2.9.4\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will fulfill obligations detailed in any applicable NASA Memorandum of Understanding (MOU)",
    "requirement": "2.9.4"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "c405ecae-3960-4e38-97ef-cb59a9538277.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n2.10.1\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will monitor the system and ensure continuous operation",
    "requirement": "2.10.1"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "21724306-9d57-4028-a940-4fa1addf39a7.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 4\n\n## ID\nL4.GEN.4\n\n### Requirement\nThe system shall enable monitoring of component health",
    "requirement": "L4.GEN.4"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "fe86abb5-f0ad-4c8d-8626-1ac4de27af31.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.GEN.8\n\n### Requirement\nServices shall provide an interface to enable monitoring of the service's health",
    "requirement": "L5.GEN.8"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "d64beaa1-8e0a-4e4c-9f4c-a08c706cc9ba.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n2.10.2\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will identify and adopt technology standards for the implementation and operations of the entire PDS system",
    "requirement": "2.10.2"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "24faf786-1237-4768-991f-fc818d83c279.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 4\n\n## ID\nL4.GEN.7\n\n### Requirement\nThe system shall control access to component interfaces that allow for ingestion or modification of data",
    "requirement": "L4.GEN.7"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "56ed2043-9511-47a5-9b6b-6995fdcd62e1.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.GEN.10\n\n### Requirement\nComponents shall control access to interfaces that alter content",
    "requirement": "L5.GEN.10"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "d346dc51-ad62-436c-b05a-7f2f7d0b655d.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n2.10.3\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will ensure that appropriate mechanisms are in place to prevent unauthorized users from compromising the integrity of PDS systems and data",
    "requirement": "2.10.3"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "24faf786-1237-4768-991f-fc818d83c279.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 4\n\n## ID\nL4.GEN.7\n\n### Requirement\nThe system shall control access to component interfaces that allow for ingestion or modification of data contained within the system.",
    "requirement": "L4.GEN.7"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "56ed2043-9511-47a5-9b6b-6995fdcd62e1.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.GEN.10\n\n### Requirement\nComponents shall control access to interfaces that alter content.",
    "requirement": "L5.GEN.10"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "eb50d620-f81f-48ed-a077-612f8b5d93dc.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 4\n\n## ID\nL4.SEC.1\n\n### Requirement\nThe system shall authorize access to system interfaces that allow for ingestion or modification of data contained within the system.",
    "requirement": "L4.SEC.1"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "6e46bc14-7298-4d7b-bc16-de9a7a075835.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SEC.1\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall authenticate a user given identifying credentials for that user.",
    "requirement": "L5.SEC.1"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "b9f1866f-2234-4362-8d2d-b58547956516.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SEC.2\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall encrypt the transmission of identifying credentials across the network.",
    "requirement": "L5.SEC.2"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "b84ddf66-d4ed-466f-9a96-9063af3cb3e8.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SEC.3\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall authorize an authenticated user for access to a controlled capability.",
    "requirement": "L5.SEC.3"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "a0d1eb81-a1a7-4179-8fe8-21c6fa1a1b61.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 4\n\n## ID\nL4.SEC.2\n\n### Requirement\nThe system shall maintain a list of authorized users.",
    "requirement": "L4.SEC.2"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "6374e319-c44f-4631-9abb-834c51abc8bb.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SEC.4\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall allow an operator of the system to create, update or delete a user identity.",
    "requirement": "L5.SEC.4"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "8716f09d-733a-4bda-96fa-48c64c3d45c2.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SEC.5\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall capture identifying information associated with a user identity.",
    "requirement": "L5.SEC.5"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "a4c29ded-e3cb-4906-9507-0f37616ca265.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SEC.6\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall allow an operator of the system to create, update or delete a group identity.",
    "requirement": "L5.SEC.6"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "3dc897d0-840d-4f07-a6de-e7a752bb44b3.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SEC.7\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall allow an operator of the system to add or remove a user from a group.",
    "requirement": "L5.SEC.7"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "3b4c2e46-fb1e-4e8a-917a-6314f8182a14.1",
