    "requirement": "3.1.1"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "53e3ff64-5bb0-4635-abcf-5b5e584e90fe.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 4\n\n## ID\nL4.QRY.1\n\n### Requirement\nThe system shall provide the capability to search for and identify artifacts registered with the PDS.",
    "requirement": "L4.QRY.1"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "1f9c4e4d-059b-47fb-bd41-f761fffaacf9.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.REG.14\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall allow queries for registered artifacts.",
    "requirement": "L5.REG.14"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "7853526d-23a6-478f-a011-511003158de1.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SCH.1\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall provide a user interface for entering of queries and display of search results accessible from a standards-compliant web browser.",
    "requirement": "L5.SCH.1"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "f3038361-b395-4f0f-8f39-499b514c8030.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SCH.2\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall degrade gracefully on browsers that lack modern features and not depend on them for operation.",
    "requirement": "L5.SCH.2"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "c3f7e1f9-85df-49de-95c1-f86efe41ec46.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SCH.4\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall provide a programmatic interface for entering of queries and return of search results that communicates over HTTP for use by client applications developed by PDS, PDS nodes, and others.",
    "requirement": "L5.SCH.4"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "b8752ee0-0c2c-4af9-8e85-976acdc42739.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SCH.5\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall provide the capability to retrieve metadata associated with registered artifacts for the purpose of generating search indexes.",
    "requirement": "L5.SCH.5"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "93e98dda-b351-4a4c-95c8-fdf0ea2b3dab.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SCH.6\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall support searching by accepting criteria as a sequence of open text keywords.",
    "requirement": "L5.SCH.6"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "d414c764-03cc-47d7-8b68-a564b3fd5635.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SCH.7\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall support searching by accepting criteria as a series of values for constraints on specified indexes.",
    "requirement": "L5.SCH.7"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "91dc536b-bd47-4c77-b5ab-ca663b85841a.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SCH.8\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall support narrowing of additional index results based on specifications of terms and/or values on indexes.",
    "requirement": "L5.SCH.8"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "fbc59d18-4ebd-4521-a423-f418bd792592.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SCH.9\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall support the ordering of results based on specified criteria including relevance and specified indexes.",
    "requirement": "L5.SCH.9"
  },
