  },
  {
    "uuid": "27671c67-1821-4d07-ae13-b4826072d5e3.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 5\n\n## ID\nL5.SCH.11\n\n### Requirement\nThe service shall annotate each URI of a result with metadata describing the URI.",
