  {
    "uuid": "4eea91cc-97a0-4104-a2bd-550896d733f1.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n4.1.2\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will develop and implement procedures for periodically ensuring the integrity of the data",
    "requirement": "4.1.2"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "7c4a0bc4-59b3-4997-802e-2edbf912bc2f.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n4.1.3\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will develop and implement procedures for periodically refreshing the data by updating the underlying storage technology",
    "requirement": "4.1.3"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "fbad1c8d-daf5-4250-a7c8-1251613b32a7.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n4.1.4\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will develop and implement a disaster recovery plan for the archive",
    "requirement": "4.1.4"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "286c9987-0cff-4f14-90b8-c231c70e0c57.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n4.1.5\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will meet U.S. federal regulations for preservation and management of the data through its Memorandum of Understanding (MOU) with the National Space Science Data Center (NSSDC)",
    "requirement": "4.1.5"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "35e25b79-8411-48c7-a960-6b03e3738d9b.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n4.2.1\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will define and maintain a set of usability requirements to ensure ongoing utility of the data in the archive",
    "requirement": "4.2.1"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "2fd4f73e-eb58-49a0-ae41-5fc33e0bd55a.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n4.2.2\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will develop and implement procedures for periodically monitoring the user community interests and practices and verifying the usability of the products in the archive",
    "requirement": "4.2.2"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "03c99c9c-9beb-4c3b-81bb-f699f7e3724b.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n4.2.3\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will monitor the evolution of technology including physical media, storage, and software in an effort to keep the archiving technology decisions relevant within the PDS",
    "requirement": "4.2.3"
  },
  {
    "uuid": "47978eb8-2aa3-43eb-81f8-e103d49d1f07.1",
    "chunk": "# Level\nLevel 3\n\n## ID\n4.2.4\n\n### Requirement\nPDS will provide a mechanism to upgrade products or data sets which do not meet usability requirements (e.g., data sets from old missions)",
    "requirement": "4.2.4"
  }
]